{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then other-- the other dog was called Caesar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was a true leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you know, right now, I'm always afraid of dogs, because we used to bicycling, bicycle tours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the dogs were running after our bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But at age three, I loved those dogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, you know, then when I was at the kindergarten age, the-- my mother knew when I come home, because the Albo, Lupo, and Caesar were waiting by the gate.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then they would-- they would-- they would come with me to the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would accompany me to the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I loved those dogs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then I would give them-- my would stuffed cabbage-- I would steal stuffed cabbage to give to Caesar.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because he was my favorite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But then I have also other memories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "At that time, my uncle had a-- had-- had a-- fencing-- a room there where he was living in-- on those premises.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he had a room where he was teaching fencing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I will-- if you ask me, I will talk to you about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Herman, which means-- you know what Herman means?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Herman, if you have on the Hebrew name is Tzvi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it means deer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moses, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a manager of a large engine factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- these were the times I was talking to you previously when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then when I got to the-- to-- to the first elementary school, already the Jewish persecution was starting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the best times when I was a real young child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so then he could not be anymore manager, because no Jews were allowed to be managers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he-- he was accountant, a chief accountant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then he couldn't be any more chief accountant.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
